---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy — Executive Choral Conducting Training"
  description="Privacy policy for Executive Choral Conducting Training (ECT). How we collect, use, and protect your personal data."
>
  <section class="page-header">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="prose">
        <p><em>Last updated: March 2026</em></p>

        <h2>Who we are</h2>
        <p>Executive Choral Conducting Training (ECT) operates the website executivechoraltraining.com. This privacy policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your personal data when you visit our website or use our services.</p>

        <h2>What data we collect</h2>
        <p>We may collect the following information:</p>
        <ul style="list-style: disc; padding-left: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
          <li>Name, email address, and company name (when you submit an enquiry form)</li>
          <li>Booking information (when you schedule a consultation via Cal.com)</li>
          <li>Website usage data via cookies (with your consent)</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>How we use your data</h2>
        <p>We use your personal data to:</p>
        <ul style="list-style: disc; padding-left: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
          <li>Respond to your enquiries and provide information about our services</li>
          <li>Schedule and manage consultations and bookings</li>
          <li>Improve our website and understand how visitors use it</li>
          <li>Comply with legal obligations</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Third-party services</h2>
        <p>We use the following third-party services:</p>
        <ul style="list-style: disc; padding-left: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
          <li><strong>Web3Forms</strong> — to process contact form submissions. Data is transmitted securely over HTTPS.</li>
          <li><strong>Cal.com</strong> — to manage consultation bookings.</li>
          <li><strong>Google Analytics</strong> — to understand website traffic (only with your cookie consent).</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Cookies</h2>
        <p>We use cookies to analyse website traffic. When you first visit our site, you will be shown a cookie consent banner. Analytics cookies are only activated if you accept. You can withdraw consent at any time by clearing your browser cookies.</p>

        <h2>Your rights</h2>
        <p>Under the UK GDPR, you have the right to:</p>
        <ul style="list-style: disc; padding-left: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
          <li>Access the personal data we hold about you</li>
          <li>Request correction of inaccurate data</li>
          <li>Request deletion of your data</li>
          <li>Object to processing of your data</li>
          <li>Request a copy of your data in a portable format</li>
        </ul>
        <p>To exercise any of these rights, contact us at <a href="mailto:office@executivechoraltraining.com">office@executivechoraltraining.com</a>.</p>

        <h2>Data retention</h2>
        <p>We retain enquiry data for as long as necessary to respond to your request and manage our relationship with you. We do not sell your data to third parties.</p>

        <h2>Contact</h2>
        <p>If you have questions about this policy, contact us at <a href="mailto:office@executivechoraltraining.com">office@executivechoraltraining.com</a>.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
